{"tid":202622,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"羅天池底橫誘惑　老婆嚇親︰做乜咁癲！有冇着底褲？","createTime":"2017-04-15T15:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T04:08:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3dfa5113f0bfd7ae64fbf555dceb62cc56ebbf","tid":202622,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"發佈日期：2017年4月15日<br />\n嘩！嘩！嘩！羅天池受了甚麼剌激？竟然來個底橫誘惑。他說太太知道他拍攝這輯相後反應很大︰「影完老婆知道後嘲笑我，因為張相望落去似冇着褲，你咁癲！我話梗係唔係，我有着底褲的，不過嗰個位置打了陰影。攝影師王穎說不如影一些不同的，不要來來去去都是打，我就試一試。」<br />\n<br />\n羅天池離開大台後，終於發圍，於網絡電影《命運老虎機》做男一，更做埋監製與武指，十分爭氣。另外有齣《救贖》，都是男主角，除了他，還有吳岱融、古明華與朱璇。離開大台膽大了，所以羅天池乜都夠膽試！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eXYycIJpPN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeXYycIJpPN0&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=a7586bf5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eXYycIJpPN0</a>"},{"pid":"d93a6ea6e60657ca58ed6340f931cb1ed5c1dda5","tid":202622,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfffb47c85b92cfb1180a636fff900fc3af22408","tid":202622,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"其實幾型 執執佢都可以嘗試下唔同角色"},{"pid":"0dc4e4ae2587a25566a067f027b102a1d958acb7","tid":202622,"uid":25689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:20:50.000Z","msg":"又幾型仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝佢好運"},{"pid":"26f6f6dc7631bd1aca118bd871b66fd459e802ca","tid":202622,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T16:26:52.000Z","msg":"有運既話係下個黑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc5075554134d1029a1d594f95e4d6c3a4bdcbd9","tid":202622,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:04:02.000Z","msg":"<img